in a unique position these days in washington in terms of 
access and influence 
the fact that we are able to get attention to canadian 
concerns when we want to speaks well for continued economic 
growth in canada as well as providing us with an opportunity of 
influence in helping address some of the more pressing 
international issues burney said 
