needs any more authority to regulate we dont think it makes 
any sense to divert their scarce resources to an industry that has 
a demonstrated safety record 
petrina noted that government regulations do require that 
ingredients of personalcare products be listed on the labels of 
retail products sold to consumers noncommercial products sold for 
professional use in business establishments such as beauty salons 
are exempt from that requirement 
