a historian has emerged as hungarys 
most powerful political figure after leading to electoral victory a 
conservative party that appeals to the hungarian pride long stifled 
under the communists 
jozsef antall 58 dominates the hungarian democratic forum 
which has been vilified by critics as nationalistic and 
