they say the partys emphasis on traditional hungarian values 
including a strong sense of the hungarian nation that extends to 
minorities outside the countrys frontiers has been misunderstood 
nevertheless the forum may be courting trouble with its 
militant championing of hungarian minority rights in neighboring 
countries 
