parliamentary elections antall told a cheering crowd on monday 
that his government will be the spokesman of 15 million hungarians 
he was referring not only to hungarys 11 million people but to 
those in neighboring countries mainly romania who became 
foreign citizens after the 1920 trianon peace treaty 
last month romania was the site of the most violent 
antihungarian riots in recent memory its leaders are already 
worried about hungarian interference and may not be keen on the 
idea of more intense scrutiny of the fate of hungarians within its 
borders 
yugoslavia the soviet union and czechoslovakia also home to 
