once in office the forum may have no choice but to change its 
priorities and deal with specter of economic collapse 
a foreign debt of more than 20 billion growing unemployment 
and doubledigit inflation are some of the most worrisome legacies 
of centralized economic planning that must be dealt with as 
hungarys new leaders embrace free market reforms 
from its inception in september 1987 at the outset of the 
democratization process that led to the elections the centerright 
democratic forum incorporated three major trends a strong 
national consciousness christian democracy and economic liberalism 
in the elections the forum captured 165 of the 386 
parliamentary seats at stake and is expected to forge a governing 
coalition with the smallholders party and christian democrats that 
would control nearly 60 percent of the legislature 
as little as a year ago jozsef antall was a virtual unknown 
a man of patrician bearing antall was born april 8 1932 a 
scion of the landed gentry his father was a widely respected 
leader of the independent smallholders party and the democratic 
forum embraces many of the prewar smallholder ideas 
the young antall studied law economics and history and was 
teaching high school when the antistalinist revolt broke out in 
1956 only to be crushed by soviet tanks 
active on the side of the revolutionaries he took part in the 
brief revival of the the smallholders party in a january magazine 
interview he called the revolution a pivotal event in his life 
after the revolution he was arrested and barred from teaching 
he later gained employment as a librarian and in 1964 joined the 
semmelweis medical history museum to be made its director 10 years 
later 
although invited antall did not attend the founding meeting of 
the democratic forum because he was outside the country but he 
became intensely involved soon after the partys creation refusing 
leadership posts with both the revived smallholders and the 
christian democrats 
he was elected forum leader in october 
antall the politician seeks to project the image of a 
thoughtful benign wise surrogate father the forums main 
campaign slogan was calm force 
even his political rivals gave him top marks for his performance 
in the talks last year between a coalition of leading opposition 
groups and the thenruling communist party 
