of other captives 
however us officials in washington were critical of frances 
warm words for gadhafi the officials who spoke on the condition 
of anonymity said france and other countries should press libya to 
expel abu nidal and his group and stop alleged efforts to make 
chemical weapons 
france is being nicer to libya than we think they should be 
said one us official 
