frenchmade mirage jet fighters that had been in france for repairs 
since 1986 the return of the planes was blocked by an embargo 
imposed when libya and france backed opposing sides during the 
civil war in chad 
in december libya pressing for delivery of the aircraft 
closed its ports to french ships 
