about paying his april apartment rent 
ive cut my prices by a third but no ones bought anything in 
two days he said 
dozens of ragged boys once lined the bustling square shining 
and repairing shoes carlinhos a droopy eyed barefoot beggar 
flicked his wrist and said they went people forget about shoes 
when things get tight 
