jorling said the biggest recalcitrants in the corporate 
world are in the auto industry 
they say they cant meet requirements on emission standards 
cant build cars with better gas mileage but its crucial that 
they be turned around because of their huge effect on the 
environment energy use global warming air pollution jorling 
