premium revenues a bit more than farmers 
in order for goldsmith to proceed with his bid the british 
takeover panel has said he must gain clearance for his plans for 
farmers in each of the nine states in which farmers operates an 
insurance company 
on monday california regulators ruled strongly that 
policyholders interests would not be served by a takeover of bat 
