<TEXT>
ast research inc a small us computer 
maker is invading japan with a clone of that countrys most 
popular personal computer a rare attack on a market dominated by 
domestic machines 
the ast computer to be unveiled wednesday in tokyo runs programs 
designed for nec corps pc9801 but can be switched over to the 
different operating system used by ibm corp it will be the first 
pc in japan to run both systems and ast says it will be priced 
competitively with nec computers 
